Base:Descriptions.Base:Description: plump red-brown hen

A plump, medium-sized, red-brown feathered hen. She has placid black eyes, a large well-shaped head capped with a red comb, full-breasted, square body with a broad back that ends in a beautiful tail of glossy dark brown feathers. Gold hackle feathers striped with black set off the hen's sturdy neck and tail.
A plump, medium-sized, red-brown feathered hen with black eyes and red comb.
